room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by The Wreck Room Escape Game in Denver
room_description: There are rumors of an alien power source that can power the world for thousands of generations. Only problem is there are very powerful people doing everything they can to make sure it never gets out. You and your team need to discover the truth, expose the lies and extract the power source. Do you have what it takes to risk everything for the greater good?
